{"tid":1640231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Popo又推篤灰熱線","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T19:44:59.000Z","uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e424af66116d245db4f7a7709d1cb9f63feb9a37","tid":1640231,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:34:44.000Z","msg":"警方今午（8日）再召開記者會，交代反修訂《逃犯條例》行動情況。資訊系統部高級警司陳志勇公布，警方重設「反暴力報料熱線」，新增電話號碼、電郵、WeChat及Line平台接受市民報料；但早前推出4日即被全數移除的WhatsApp報料熱線，陳志勇稱因WhatsApp公司不同意警方使用該平台，故今次無用該平台設立報料熱線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新增報料熱線電話為5333 3103；WeChat ID為HKPF53333103；Line ID為hkpf53333103；電郵為hotline@police.gov.hk。警方表示，有關平台將不會使用自動化回覆，亦非用作報案平台，市民若需報案，應到就近警署或致電999。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191008/s00001/1570524858985/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e8%ad%a6%e5%af%9f%e5%a0%b1%e6%96%99%e7%86%b1%e7%b7%9a%e3%80%8c%e7%bf%bb%e7%94%9f%e3%80%8d-%e5%a2%9ewechat-line%e7%84%a1whatsapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191008%2Fs00001%2F1570524858985%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25af%259f%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%2586%25b1%25e7%25b7%259a%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25bf%25bb%25e7%2594%259f%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%25a2%259ewechat-line%25e7%2584%25a1whatsapp&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=052a6d8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191008%2Fs00001%2F1570524858985%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25af%259f%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%2586%25b1%25e7%25b7%259a%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25bf%25bb%25e7%2594%259f%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%25a2%259ewechat-line%25e7%2584%25a1whatsapp&h=9a467767\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.c